#timeline 
# Haven Irregulars
A timeline of key events in the history of Antheros and Haven.

![[~attachments/DnDLine.png]]

```timeline
[line-3, body-2]
+ Year 1
+ Declaration of the 2nd Namori Empire
+ With the surrender of Emor, the Namori Empire completed its western expansion and now spans two continents. In celebration of the event a 2nd Namori Empire is declared and a new calendar era established. [[Timeline/Antheros/Declaration of the 2nd Namori Empire|Full article]]

+ Year 997
+ Freeing of Haven
+ The Free City of Haven was given its charter as an independent city-state by the crumbling Namori Empire which was retreating to the east. [[Timeline/Antheros/Freeing of Haven|Full article]]

+ 1171-15-13
+ The Burning of Rogue's Roost
+ On this day, the home of the Haven Thieves' Guild, Rogue's Roost, was burned down, leaving the guild homeless. [[Timeline/Antheros/The Burning of Rogue's Roost|Full article]]
  
+ 1172-6-8
+ Creation of the Haven Irregulars
+ The first official day for this new unit in the Haven City Watch. [[Timeline/Antheros/Creation of the Haven Irregulars|Full article]]

+ 1172-6-9
+ 1st Patrol
+ 1st day of patrol for the squad [[Timeline/Antheros/1st Patrol|Full article]] 
  
```

